citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:58 PM on
12-Sep-16.
The inspector arrived at the property and knocked at the front door of the park office. The inspector then contacted
a facility representative via phone. The facility representative stated that there wasn't anyone available for an
inspection today.
